Package: tm.plugin.sentiment
Imports: slam
Maintainer: Mario Annau <mario.annau@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Title: Text corpus sentiment analysis
Author: Mario Annau <mario.annau@gmail.com>
Description: tm.plugin.sentiment supports sentiment analysis of text
    corpora. Scoring of text documents, build up of sentiment time
    series in xts and charting using facilities of quantmod are
    supported.
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2010-08-09
Depends: tm, quantmod
Collate: 'OHCLSent.transformations.R' 'addSentiment.R'
    'chartSentiment.R' 'corpus.R' 'data.R' 'getRelevant.R' 'metaXTS.R'
    'preprocessCorpus.R' 'score.R'
